    "We design a CAF module based on the SE block for effective feature combination between the dual encoders.",
    "Specifically, the module selectively emphasizes important features from both encoders, improving the integration of high-level and local information. 3.",
    "We leverage the MLP-Mixer model that depends solely on MLPs to perform BUS images classification.",
    "The latter is being used for the first time for this task, to the best of our knowledge.",
    "We demonstrate the capabilities of both ViTs and MLP-Mixer in accurately classifying BUS images, with ViTs relying on attention mechanisms and MLP-Mixer relying exclusively on MLPs.Computer-aided diagnosis (CAD) systems are increasingly utilized to aid healthcare professionals in diagnosing various diseases and cancers, including breast cancer."
